OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright end
OL,6,Fto the day then a dry night with long
OL,7,Fclear spells. Becoming chilly in the
OL,8,Feast with a touch of frost and patchy
OL,9,Ffog.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FAnother dry and bright day
OL,12,Fwith long periods of sunshine. A
OL,13,Fchilly start then becoming quite warm
OL,14,Fby the afternoon. Some patchy mist may
OL,15,Faffect the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
