OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry on
OL,6,FSaturday with sunny spells, but cooler
OL,7,Fand cloudier in the northeast. Mainly
OL,8,Fdry and bright on Sunday and Monday
OL,9,Fbut some patchy rain possible in the
OL,10,Ffar north.
